data.description: Charming home in a prime location, just moments from pristine beaches, shopping & restaurants. This delightful property boasts a newer roof and energy-efficient solar panels, fully paid off at closing, guaranteeing minimal utility costs between $30 to $40 per month. Enjoy eco-friendly amenities including a solar water heater and an updated HVAC system installed in 2018. The interior features new luxury vinyl plank flooring added in 2020 & newer appliances from 2023, along with freshly paint. A spacious two-car garage and a large master suite with a dual-vanity bathroom, water closet, and expansive walk-in closet add to the home's appeal. Set on a half-acre lot, the residence offers a fenced backyard with sprinkler system & screened patio, perfect for relaxing and entertaining.
